    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/0efd5d5f6ee30cffd9273b494be3a54c.avif?t=1759052688\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个游戏中，您将化身为一只机智聪明的猫猫工程师，您的目标是帮助世界各国的房子都能发亮，为它们提供足够的电力。游戏内有许多不同国家的房子，例如香港、台湾、埃及等，每个国家都有其独特的房屋风格和布局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/5f58df50af89ba38a3dbb8debb3f4a3f.poster.avif?t=1759052688\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/5f58df50af89ba38a3dbb8debb3f4a3f.webm?t=1759052688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/5f58df50af89ba38a3dbb8debb3f4a3f.mp4?t=1759052688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >帮助世界各地的房子亮起来</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摆放或移除电线，令所有房子都能亮起来，但要小心，不要令房子电力超过负荷!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/2306d1220c11e6c59a7b7345272ca0fe.avif?t=1759052688\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过120道待解谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽力通过所有主线关卡，在每个城市都有着不同的电缆问题等你来解决，即使你有着猫程师的脑袋也能将你难倒!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/cac43d69092ffc2971b10a62e3fbe4d5.avif?t=1759052688\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特别的电力工具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用地下隧道能将电力远程传输，电力加倍器令电力加倍，改向器能令电线转弯，还有更多器具等你来发掘</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/3a70fe6942e0324e6862f71d9ba06a1d.avif?t=1759052688\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >温馨的画面与游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然电线问题很困难，但是画面和游戏是绝对的温馨，每完成一个城市就能解锁更多画册和图像</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/b104e54593855bdd3432fcb42dd4b086.poster.avif?t=1759052688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/b104e54593855bdd3432fcb42dd4b086.webm?t=1759052688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2316640/extras/b104e54593855bdd3432fcb42dd4b086.mp4?t=1759052688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
